@node "History" "History"
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
                                    @{b}HISTORY@{ub}
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

 @{b}Version 1.0@{ub}

 - First release
 - Uses copperscreen

 @{b}Version 2.0@{ub}

 - Replaced copperscreen by 256-color-screen
 - Landscape generator rewritten
 - Improved mouse control

 @{b}Version 2.5@{ub}

 - Engine completely rewritten
 - Real perspective
 - OS friendly
 - Selectable screen modes
 - Different heights
@endnode

@node "Future" "Future"
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
                                     @{b}FUTURE@{ub}
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

 - Bigger and more realistic landscape
 - X/Z-Axis rotation
 - Drawing sky using spherical mapping
 - Reflections in the water
 - Variable resolution
 - Selectable detail levels
 - Graphic card support
@endnode

